    "created_at": "2015-12-12T10:47:43Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-12T11:28:42Z",
    "body": "I noticed that the crash is caused because Electron tries to call callbacks that are not in runtime anymore. I searched for a method which deletes the association with these callbacks and found `removeAllListeners()` in the documentation of Node.js (https://nodejs.org/api/events.html#events_emitter_removealllisteners_event). That's the story :smiley: \n"
  },
